                <h3>Build, Share and Play</h3>
                <p>The AnalogKit interface has to accomplish two very different tasks - building and tweaking projects, and then performing with those modules in a live environment. My solution was a 'play mode' where modules and connections locked into position and the user could treat their iPad more like a conventional piece of music hardware.</p>
