                <h3>Modular Audio Building</h3>
                <p>AnalogKit ships with dozens of modules and interface components that users can wire together in any way they choose. My goal was to create modules that were easy to tell apart from one another, easy to interact with in a hurry, and efficient in their use of space.</p>
